1
00:00:09,540 --> 00:00:10,340
Xiyin.

2
00:00:11,140 --> 00:00:12,740
I never imagined our last parting

3
00:00:13,700 --> 00:00:14,980
would be final.

4
00:00:19,260 --> 00:00:20,060
Xiyin.

5
00:00:28,820 --> 00:00:29,620
Xiyin.

6
00:00:29,860 --> 00:00:30,660
Xiyin.

7
00:00:30,860 --> 00:00:31,660
Xiyin!

8
00:01:03,920 --> 00:01:06,760
[Immortal Beyond Dust]
[Episode 2]

9
00:01:08,900 --> 00:01:09,500
Don't move.

10
00:01:12,060 --> 00:01:12,860
Straighten your back.

11
00:01:14,020 --> 00:01:15,060
Raise your hand a little higher.

12
00:01:15,900 --> 00:01:16,900
Bring your leg forward a bit.

13
00:01:18,600 --> 00:01:19,960
[Bai Ruoxi, Embodiment of Xieyun]

14
00:01:26,300 --> 00:01:27,340
What are you doing here?

15
00:01:27,580 --> 00:01:28,740
I've come to take her away.

16
00:01:31,540 --> 00:01:32,380
Go back to your room.

17
00:01:40,660 --> 00:01:41,460
Xiyin.

18
00:01:44,340 --> 00:01:45,220
Is that you?

19
00:01:45,260 --> 00:01:46,060
You bad guy!

20
00:02:00,060 --> 00:02:00,980
You're not her.

21
00:02:03,220 --> 00:02:05,140
What have you done to Xiyin?

22
00:02:05,580 --> 00:02:06,540
This has nothing to do with you!

23
00:02:07,780 --> 00:02:08,660
Nothing to do with me?

24
00:02:10,180 --> 00:02:12,380
Xiyin and I grew up together.

25
00:02:13,140 --> 00:02:14,140
She

26
00:02:14,940 --> 00:02:15,740
was protecting you

27
00:02:16,900 --> 00:02:18,420
even until death.

28
00:02:19,620 --> 00:02:20,540
And you?

29
00:02:21,860 --> 00:02:22,660
You

30
00:02:23,180 --> 00:02:24,180
used a fiend

31
00:02:24,180 --> 00:02:25,180
to resurrect a monster

32
00:02:25,180 --> 00:02:26,540
that looks just like her!

33
00:02:27,260 --> 00:02:28,380
I really regret

34
00:02:28,380 --> 00:02:29,900
not killing you!

35
00:02:30,740 --> 00:02:31,620
If I had, Xiyin

36
00:02:32,660 --> 00:02:34,220
wouldn't have died because of you!

37
00:02:34,940 --> 00:02:35,820
You're right.

38
00:02:36,860 --> 00:02:38,180
I'm the one who caused her death.

39
00:02:38,940 --> 00:02:39,780
That's why

40
00:02:40,180 --> 00:02:41,740
I must bring her back, no matter what.

41
00:02:42,740 --> 00:02:44,420
Even if it means eternal damnation,

42
00:02:45,180 --> 00:02:46,740
I'll do it.

43
00:02:46,980 --> 00:02:48,140
You're insane!

44
00:02:57,780 --> 00:02:58,180
It's alright.

45
00:02:58,900 --> 00:02:59,940
He's not a bad person.

46
00:03:00,420 --> 00:03:01,060
He's

47
00:03:02,340 --> 00:03:03,580
a friend of my master.

48
00:03:06,140 --> 00:03:07,380
We're just sparring with our magic.

49
00:03:08,460 --> 00:03:09,660
If you don't want to go inside,

50
00:03:10,580 --> 00:03:11,660
stand a bit further back,

51
00:03:11,820 --> 00:03:12,580
alright?

52
00:03:15,460 --> 00:03:17,100
Do you remember the mantra I taught you?

53
00:03:19,900 --> 00:03:20,580
Man...

54
00:03:20,940 --> 00:03:21,580
Mantra?

55
00:03:22,860 --> 00:03:24,620
Xieyun is indeed within her.

56
00:03:25,580 --> 00:03:26,380
No.

57
00:03:27,260 --> 00:03:29,060
The Immortal Venerable
must never know about this.

58
00:03:29,380 --> 00:03:30,980
I'm taking her away.

59
00:03:31,180 --> 00:03:32,100
You can't take her away!

60
00:03:32,380 --> 00:03:33,380
Without Xieyun,

61
00:03:33,820 --> 00:03:35,580
you're just
a low-level immortal disciple.

62
00:03:36,020 --> 00:03:36,980
How can you protect her?

63
00:03:38,180 --> 00:03:38,980
Let go!

64
00:03:57,180 --> 00:03:58,780
Just pretend you didn't see anything.

65
00:03:58,980 --> 00:03:59,700
Go!

66
00:04:00,460 --> 00:04:01,180
Just go!

67
00:04:28,420 --> 00:04:29,100
It's alright now.

68
00:04:31,860 --> 00:04:32,460
It hurts.

69
00:04:33,500 --> 00:04:34,180
Not at all.

70
00:04:34,180 --> 00:04:36,520
♪What is flickering?♪

71
00:04:37,180 --> 00:04:37,980
Master.

72
00:04:37,980 --> 00:04:39,260
♪Shining, delicate, and bright♪

73
00:04:39,420 --> 00:04:45,260
♪Like a trace of bitterness in a smile♪

74
00:04:45,300 --> 00:04:48,140
♪What is falling?♪

75
00:04:48,580 --> 00:04:51,380
♪Clean, precise, and light♪

76
00:04:51,620 --> 00:04:56,820
♪Like enduring too many farewells♪

77
00:04:57,740 --> 00:04:59,340
♪When petals drift down♪

78
00:04:59,380 --> 00:05:00,840
♪When the rain falls all around♪

79
00:05:00,940 --> 00:05:03,540
♪I gaze into your eyes♪

80
00:05:03,700 --> 00:05:05,400
♪Beyond the dunes♪

81
00:05:05,500 --> 00:05:06,780
♪No end in sight♪

82
00:05:06,780 --> 00:05:09,780
♪I am like a mayfly♪

83
00:05:09,940 --> 00:05:11,340
♪I won't ask what the future holds♪

84
00:05:11,380 --> 00:05:12,840
♪Nor will I run away♪

85
00:05:12,860 --> 00:05:15,800
♪Through all seasons by my side♪

86
00:05:15,800 --> 00:05:21,060
♪Searching for sparks in the dust♪

87
00:05:47,460 --> 00:05:48,260
Wake up.

88
00:05:49,380 --> 00:05:50,180
Wake up.

89
00:05:59,380 --> 00:06:00,180
What's wrong?

90
00:06:01,020 --> 00:06:01,820
It hurts.

91
00:06:08,660 --> 00:06:09,620
The pain is gone.

92
00:06:16,820 --> 00:06:17,940
This isn't food.

93
00:06:18,500 --> 00:06:19,220
It's an herb.

94
00:06:20,340 --> 00:06:21,620
It can heal your wounds.

95
00:06:23,340 --> 00:06:24,340
Herb?

96
00:06:27,460 --> 00:06:28,260
That's right.

97
00:06:28,980 --> 00:06:29,780
Herb.

98
00:06:30,420 --> 00:06:32,020
Herb.

99
00:06:45,140 --> 00:06:45,940
Young Lord,

100
00:06:46,540 --> 00:06:47,500
Yaoyang has been spending

101
00:06:47,620 --> 00:06:48,860
these past few days happily
with that woman.

102
00:06:49,340 --> 00:06:50,300
He doesn't seem concerned

103
00:06:50,580 --> 00:06:51,620
about the task you gave him at all.

104
00:06:52,380 --> 00:06:53,220
Looks like

105
00:06:53,220 --> 00:06:54,180
[Gu Li, Young Lord of the Shadow Clan]

106
00:06:54,180 --> 00:06:56,500
it's time someone gave them
a little push.

107
00:06:57,140 --> 00:06:57,980
Also,

108
00:06:57,980 --> 00:06:59,780
we've made some progress on the matter

109
00:06:59,780 --> 00:07:00,660
you asked us to investigate.

110
00:07:01,940 --> 00:07:02,780
Spill it.

111
00:07:03,020 --> 00:07:04,060
We've found her.

112
00:07:04,420 --> 00:07:06,140
In this life, she is called Wan'er.

113
00:07:06,420 --> 00:07:07,260
She's a mortal woman.

114
00:07:08,380 --> 00:07:09,460
But...

115
00:07:11,880 --> 00:07:14,280
[Wan'er, Demon Clan]

116
00:07:25,220 --> 00:07:25,860
Who are you?

117
00:07:26,140 --> 00:07:27,260
Why did you save me?

118
00:07:27,340 --> 00:07:28,940
You really haven't changed a bit.

119
00:07:36,260 --> 00:07:37,060
Martial Uncle.

120
00:07:38,060 --> 00:07:39,500
Since High Immortal Xiyin was revived,

121
00:07:39,980 --> 00:07:42,260
she seems to be surrounded
by Xieyun's fiendish aura.

122
00:07:42,620 --> 00:07:44,620
This must be Yaoyang's doing.

123
00:07:44,820 --> 00:07:45,780
Shouldn't we report this

124
00:07:46,100 --> 00:07:47,820
to the Immortal Venerable
as soon as possible?

125
00:07:48,060 --> 00:07:49,260
The situation isn't clear yet.

126
00:07:50,220 --> 00:07:51,580
I'll report it

127
00:07:51,580 --> 00:07:52,820
after I've uncovered the truth.

128
00:07:53,660 --> 00:07:54,460
But...

129
00:08:01,540 --> 00:08:03,580
[Yuxun, Demon Clan]

130
00:08:03,580 --> 00:08:04,860
Well, well, look who it is.

131
00:08:05,260 --> 00:08:06,860
The young lord of the Shadow Clan.

132
00:08:07,700 --> 00:08:08,740
My place is humble.

133
00:08:08,900 --> 00:08:10,060
Not worthy of someone
as distinguished as you.

134
00:08:10,580 --> 00:08:11,340
I'll be leaving.

135
00:08:12,140 --> 00:08:13,860
I found her reincarnation.

136
00:08:15,580 --> 00:08:16,660
What did you say?

137
00:08:16,860 --> 00:08:17,540
Where is she?

138
00:08:20,940 --> 00:08:22,260
You're cunning.

139
00:08:22,300 --> 00:08:23,260
Don't try to trick me!

140
00:08:23,500 --> 00:08:25,140
In this life, she's called Wan'er,

141
00:08:25,540 --> 00:08:26,660
a mortal woman.

142
00:08:27,500 --> 00:08:28,300
But...

143
00:08:28,660 --> 00:08:29,460
But what?

144
00:08:30,060 --> 00:08:31,460
When I found her,

145
00:08:31,740 --> 00:08:33,180
she was about to end her own life.

146
00:08:33,700 --> 00:08:35,300
Because she has an incurable illness.

147
00:08:38,100 --> 00:08:39,100
I'm warning you,

148
00:08:39,460 --> 00:08:40,460
if you dare harm her again,

149
00:08:40,460 --> 00:08:41,580
I won't let you off!

150
00:08:42,980 --> 00:08:44,300
Don't worry.

151
00:08:45,220 --> 00:08:47,140
She's just a mortal now.

152
00:08:47,700 --> 00:08:49,260
There's nothing to exploit.

153
00:08:50,140 --> 00:08:50,900
You didn't come

154
00:08:51,340 --> 00:08:52,900
just to tell me this, did you?

155
00:08:53,340 --> 00:08:54,020
Out with it.

156
00:08:54,500 --> 00:08:55,700
What do you want?

157
00:08:56,700 --> 00:08:57,940
There is indeed something

158
00:08:58,180 --> 00:08:59,300
I need you to do.

159
00:08:59,740 --> 00:09:00,940
Let me tell you,

160
00:09:01,660 --> 00:09:03,820
I don't cheat,

161
00:09:03,820 --> 00:09:05,820
steal, fight, set fires,

162
00:09:05,820 --> 00:09:07,340
kill, seduce,

163
00:09:07,340 --> 00:09:08,580
or bully.

164
00:09:08,700 --> 00:09:10,300
I know exactly

165
00:09:10,300 --> 00:09:11,660
what you're capable of.

166
00:09:12,260 --> 00:09:14,100
And it's definitely not any of that.

167
00:09:28,020 --> 00:09:28,980
I'm doing this

168
00:09:28,980 --> 00:09:30,220
out of friendship.

169
00:09:30,540 --> 00:09:31,900
It has nothing to do with this stuff.

170
00:09:32,340 --> 00:09:32,780
Just tell me,

171
00:09:33,420 --> 00:09:34,180
what is it?

172
00:09:35,260 --> 00:09:36,260
Simple.

173
00:09:56,780 --> 00:09:57,740
It's her.

174
00:09:57,760 --> 00:09:59,000
[Tu Jing, Qingqiu]

175
00:10:19,620 --> 00:10:21,180
I feel like I've been here before.

176
00:10:27,180 --> 00:10:28,860
That hurts!

177
00:10:34,180 --> 00:10:35,300
Ow, ow, ow!

178
00:10:35,300 --> 00:10:36,660
Ouch!

179
00:10:37,460 --> 00:10:39,260
You little mushroom spirit.

180
00:10:39,620 --> 00:10:42,020
How dare to bully a young lady?

181
00:10:42,740 --> 00:10:43,540
Have mercy!

182
00:10:43,980 --> 00:10:45,860
I just wanted to try out my new magic.

183
00:10:46,220 --> 00:10:47,460
It was just a joke.

184
00:10:48,260 --> 00:10:49,700
Don't take it seriously.

185
00:10:53,220 --> 00:10:54,620
My head is spinning!

186
00:11:05,620 --> 00:11:07,020
What did you eat

187
00:11:07,180 --> 00:11:08,020
to get so strong?

188
00:11:12,420 --> 00:11:13,460
Thank you for saving me.

189
00:11:15,020 --> 00:11:15,820
No problem.

190
00:11:21,820 --> 00:11:22,620
That smells great.

191
00:11:27,460 --> 00:11:27,940
This

192
00:11:28,420 --> 00:11:30,020
is a special sachet
made by our fox clan.

193
00:11:30,900 --> 00:11:31,980
If you like it,

194
00:11:32,380 --> 00:11:33,220
it's yours.

195
00:11:33,820 --> 00:11:34,620
I like it.

196
00:11:35,940 --> 00:11:36,620
I like it too.

197
00:11:36,620 --> 00:11:37,580
I want one too.

198
00:11:37,660 --> 00:11:38,860
Can you give me one?

199
00:11:40,580 --> 00:11:41,660
I don't want it anymore.

200
00:11:43,100 --> 00:11:43,700
You

201
00:11:44,180 --> 00:11:45,220
are a mushroom?

202
00:11:46,500 --> 00:11:47,980
Not an ordinary mushroom.

203
00:11:48,420 --> 00:11:49,740
I'm a a one-of-a-kind mushroom

204
00:11:49,740 --> 00:11:51,260
from ancient times.

205
00:11:52,620 --> 00:11:53,780
A very special mushroom.

206
00:11:55,060 --> 00:11:56,500
Are mushrooms edible?

207
00:11:58,900 --> 00:11:59,700
Yes.

208
00:12:01,060 --> 00:12:02,300
What do you want?

209
00:12:02,300 --> 00:12:03,740
Can't we talk instead of fight?

210
00:12:04,140 --> 00:12:04,780
No.

211
00:12:15,500 --> 00:12:17,020
What a cute little mushroom.

212
00:12:17,620 --> 00:12:19,020
I can take it back for soup.

213
00:12:21,900 --> 00:12:22,620
Oh, right.

214
00:12:23,060 --> 00:12:24,180
Yaoyang says

215
00:12:24,420 --> 00:12:25,900
we shouldn't accept kindness
without returning it.

216
00:12:27,220 --> 00:12:28,140
Why don't you

217
00:12:28,460 --> 00:12:29,060
come home with me?

218
00:12:29,500 --> 00:12:30,300
I'll treat you to some mushrooms.

219
00:12:33,780 --> 00:12:34,580
But

220
00:12:35,660 --> 00:12:37,980
I haven't figured out
how to cook it yet.

221
00:12:38,420 --> 00:12:39,100
Miss,

222
00:12:39,740 --> 00:12:40,620
you don't know how to cook?

223
00:12:41,460 --> 00:12:43,220
Yaoyang usually does the cooking.

224
00:12:43,780 --> 00:12:45,060
But he's sick now.

225
00:12:48,180 --> 00:12:50,180
So you picked these herbs

226
00:12:51,460 --> 00:12:52,580
to save him?

227
00:12:55,220 --> 00:12:56,260
Miss, take me back with you.

228
00:12:56,820 --> 00:12:57,900
Yaoyang is my savior.

229
00:12:58,740 --> 00:12:59,460
Savior?

230
00:13:27,140 --> 00:13:29,880
♪What is flickering?♪

231
00:13:30,100 --> 00:13:32,620
♪Shining, delicate, and bright♪

232
00:13:32,780 --> 00:13:38,620
♪Like a trace of bitterness in a smile♪

233
00:13:38,660 --> 00:13:41,500
♪What is falling?♪

234
00:13:41,940 --> 00:13:44,740
♪Clean, precise, and light♪

235
00:13:44,980 --> 00:13:50,180
♪Like enduring too many farewells♪

236
00:13:51,100 --> 00:13:52,700
♪When petals drift down♪

237
00:13:52,740 --> 00:13:54,200
♪When the rain falls all around♪

238
00:13:54,300 --> 00:13:56,900
♪I gaze into your eyes♪

239
00:13:57,060 --> 00:13:58,760
♪Beyond the dunes♪

240
00:13:58,860 --> 00:14:00,140
♪No end in sight♪

241
00:14:00,140 --> 00:14:03,140
♪I am like a mayfly♪

242
00:14:03,300 --> 00:14:04,700
♪I won't ask what the future holds♪

243
00:14:04,740 --> 00:14:06,200
♪Nor will I run away♪

244
00:14:06,220 --> 00:14:09,160
♪Through all seasons by my side♪

245
00:14:09,160 --> 00:14:14,420
♪Searching for sparks in the dust♪

246
00:14:28,740 --> 00:14:31,480
♪What is flickering?♪

247
00:14:31,700 --> 00:14:34,180
♪Shining, delicate, and bright♪

248
00:14:34,380 --> 00:14:40,180
♪Like a trace of bitterness in a smile♪

249
00:14:40,620 --> 00:14:43,420
♪What is falling?♪

250
00:14:43,540 --> 00:14:46,360
♪Clean, precise, and light♪

251
00:14:46,580 --> 00:14:51,580
♪Like enduring too many farewells♪

252
00:14:52,700 --> 00:14:54,180
♪When petals drift down♪

253
00:14:54,180 --> 00:14:55,680
♪When the rain falls all around♪

254
00:14:55,780 --> 00:14:58,340
♪I gaze into your eyes♪
